    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/28109b051a195684d98c38b876d3dfb9.avif?t=1738029562\" width=460 height=214 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏说明：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/4a68631b697108cedb89a127abdd37ad.webp?t=1738029562\" width=15 height=18 /></span>： </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款街机、快节奏、休闲、可爱的猫猫弹珠游戏。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/4609ff064880150322c6f0b9761f8f1d.webp?t=1738029562\" width=15 height=18 /></span>： </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >许多挑战等你来！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/dca79d1fc48c1b5df37b36e46eb369c3.webp?t=1738029562\" width=15 height=18 /></span>： </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和猫猫一起玩耍做朋友吧！！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/5b730439c667fad0f203aa6ea6487547.webp?t=1738029562\" width=15 height=18 /></span>： </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战高分数。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/81bdeaa0f3061aac69c24a36b3df8e03.webp?t=1738029562\" width=15 height=18 /></span>： </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前5个主题，未来会免费更新游戏玩法和主题。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏模式玩法介绍：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/16f3e95ef924c9ffd4bd31b58dc874c2.webp?t=1738029562\" width=246 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不断挑战获得猫猫最高的友好度！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/da03c208c90012ca8d8e93ae3229a83b.avif?t=1738029562\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras_big/da03c208c90012ca8d8e93ae3229a83b.avif?t=1738029562 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/b9996d7a4b75600234afe4d554d104a8.webp?t=1738029562\" width=246 height=45 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在规定时间内达到目标友好度，提升LV到20获得胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/9c8ea16ea865bb61e60ed9b8e7537b3b.avif?t=1738029562\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras_big/9c8ea16ea865bb61e60ed9b8e7537b3b.avif?t=1738029562 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/9cc5f4d285429d432436689ad26c0232.webp?t=1738029562\" width=246 height=45 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >和猫猫一起钓鱼完成钓鱼图鉴吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122360/extras/f96929ed81e2bbffa2445a63eb41391e.avif?t=1738029562\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com